l Chabon</p><p>&#8220;She knew me better than anyone else in the world. And still wanted to have lunch with me.&#8221;<br>&#8212;Julian Barnes, <em>The Sense Of An Ending</em></p><p>&#8220;To find a person inexhaustible is simply the definition of love.&#8221;<br>&#8212;Iris Murdoch</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2b8c1b4d-d6e4-4cdf-a8a9-d91fdd1d360f.heic" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2b8c1b4d-d6e4-4cdf-a8a9-d91fdd1d360f.heic 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2b8c1b4d-d6e4-4cdf-a8a9-d91fdd1d360f.heic 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2b8c1b4d-d6e4-4cdf-a8a9-d91fdd1d360f.heic 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2b8c1b4d-d6e4-4cdf-a8a9-d91fdd1d360f.heic 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F2b8c1b4d-d6e4-4cdf-a8a9-d91fdd1d360f.heic" width="800" height="1052" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/2b8c1b4d-d6e4-4cdf-a8a9-d91fdd1d360f.heic&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;ima